Create 2 Folder (Frontend, Backend)

Frontend Installation
    {*If there is no project*} 
        npm create vite@latest . -- -- template react 
        npm install
    (*Else*)
    npm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/vite
    npm install react-router-dom
    npm clsx
    npm install @fontsource/inter
    npm install @heroicons/react
    npm install html2canvas
    npm install docx file-saver
    npm install js-cookie



    {/*Test*/}
    npm install --save-dev jest @testing-library/react @testing-library/jest-dom (optional)
    npm install --save-dev @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-react
    npm install --save-dev jest-environment-jsdom

Backend Installation
    npm install -g nodemon
    npm install fastify pg @fastify/cors
    npm install dotenv
    npm install googleapis pg node-cron
    npm install googleapis pg node-schedule
    npm install bcrypt
    npm install nodemailer bcryptjs crypto
    npm install jsonwebtoken
    npm install luxon
    npm install @supabase/supabase-js

